{"tid":1817528,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"雖然炒咗車，但今次路政署有回應要求，係值得認同","createTime":"2020-01-09T07:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T11:38:45.000Z","uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fb0e66468f3caadde01d424aad9aa24c02a98cbd","tid":1817528,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MfvCaTM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMfvCaTM.png&h=57a8cd1d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14z3QTO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14z3QTO.png&h=2f1af778&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRoad Research Society 道路硏究社<br />\n<br />\n馬路地面驚現簡體字？<br />\n今朝西貢區議員何偉航 Stanley HO Wai-hong post 左張相，發現路面上出現「灣」字嘅「簡體字」。大家都好自然會覺得係咪又係搞赤化，強行消滅繁體字。<br />\n<br />\n無錯，捍衞繁體字係我地嘅責任；不過其實路面上呢個疑似簡體字，其實係「繁體俗字」。因爲漢字變化多端，有舊式寫法之餘，仲有異體、俗寫。例如「台湾大哥大」用「湾」就係俗字嘅一種。<br />\n<br />\n⭐️咁係唔係赤化？⭐️<br />\n呢個情況下就唔係咁講。因爲二十年前，馬路上嘅「灣」都係咁寫；佢唔係標準嘅簡體字，因爲個「亦」字兩筆上下掉轉咗。如果你以前有留意開路面，或者都會有印象。係 1998 年杜老誌道天橋交通意外中，（畫面比較矇糊，但原諒我搵唔到一張更加淸晰嘅圖片🙏🙇🏻&zwj;♂️），「港灣道」個「湾」字就已經係咁寫～<br />\n<br />\n⭐️咁好地地做咩寫「俗字」？⭐️<br />\n呢層其實佢地唔係故意寫簡體字，而係因爲綫條比較粗嘅關係，寫唔到太複雜嘅字。因爲近年路面文字改用較幼嘅綫條，所以好多地方嘅「灣」字改返標準繁體寫法，舊式俗寫就買少見少喇。<br />\n<br />\n⭐️道路硏究社嘅回應⭐️<br />\n雖然個「湾」字唔係簡體字，而係舊式俗字。但係我地都認爲，用返標準繁體寫法最好，始終大家習慣依家個寫法。<br />\n<br />\n⭐️延伸閱讀⭐️<br />\n【維基百科】繁體俗字<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/繁體俗字\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E7%B9%81%E9%AB%94%E4%BF%97%E5%AD%97&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF0195pAf34VZm09NJx5vbAww%3D&h=1ac31bd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/繁體俗字</a><br />\n<br />\n【東方日報影片】杜老誌道天橋交通意外（影片一開始）<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20140615/00176_097.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140615%2F00176_097.html&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF0195pAf34VZm09NJx5vbAww%3D&h=59cdde4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20140615/00176_097.html</a><br />\n<br />\n#簡體字 #俗字<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a75f09e1fe008c68639df3bbcf34c85dfe15265","tid":1817528,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:17:31.000Z","msg":"長知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffded74e902db29afad346083eae45e3983ba866","tid":1817528,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cef50033cccfb25d449631e98dfa878547ebad5","tid":1817528,"uid":50094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:19:52.000Z","msg":"手足你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，小弟整左個網叫 EventVote<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkeventvote.com/overview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkeventvote.com%2Foverview&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF0195pAf34VZm09NJx5vbAww%3D&h=7f50b55b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkeventvote.com/overview</a><br />\n<br />\n《最集中最方便既活動資訊平台-HKEventVote》<br />\nlihkg link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1817084/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1817084/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n想大家有個免費平台share 唔同嘅活動📣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抗爭日程又好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聯署又好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />約一班手足去懲罰黃店都好<br />\n<br />\n網站前期冇人用冇乜event<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要麻煩大家係入面開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=